data.description: This BEAUTIFUL 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located on a corner lot of the Kinston Park community will take your breath away as soon as you walk in the door with the gorgeous beadboard entryway leading into the open concept living room and kitchen. The kitchen is the perfect space, complete with stainless steel appliances, white cabinets and plenty dining area. All three bedrooms are located on the second level with an additional loft space and a walk in laundry room. The primary bedroom contains a private bathroom with a double sink vanity and large walk in closet. The back yard is fully fenced.
